Class Donut

java.lang.Object
cafe.MenuItem
cafe.Donut
All Implemented Interfaces:
Customizable
public class Donut
extends MenuItem
implements Customizable
This class extends the MenuItem class and includes specific data and operations for a donut object, such as the donut type, flavor and the quantity
